Package: turbotoken
Title: Fast BPE Tokenizer
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("TurboToken Contributors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                   email = "turbotoken@example.com")
Description: A drop-in replacement for tiktoken providing the fastest BPE
    tokenization on every platform. Uses a Zig + hand-written assembly core
    with platform-specific SIMD backends.
